Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:58.67,default - cyan,,0,0,0,,誰の肩に止まるかな
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:58.67,Default - white,,0,0,0,,Whose shoulder will it land upon
