Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.15,0:25:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(639.195,581.834)}this is an expression of our determination
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.02,0:25:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638.389,599.19)}Without averting our eyes from hard facts,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.45,0:25:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,embrace each crisis while moving forward,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.92,0:25:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Opening the way
