Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.36,0:26:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(637.988,583.362)}An awful starting hand, well beyond saving
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.82,0:26:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If he discards a South wind, the hand will not continue
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.28,0:27:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you retreat from such a position?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.98,0:27:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Advance!
